import React from 'react'
import {Menu} from 'semantic-ui-react'


export default () => {

     return(

          <Menu style={{marginTop: '10px'}}>

               <Menu.Item>
                    CrowdCoin
               </Menu.Item>
               <Menu.Menu position="right">
                    <Menu.Item>
                         Campaigns
                    </Menu.Item>
                    <Menu.Item>
                         +
                    </Menu.Item>
                    
               </Menu.Menu>
          </Menu>
     )
}
